<item>Are the sample means for <emphasis effect="italics">n</emphasis> = 5 and <emphasis effect="italics">n</emphasis> = 10 “close” to the theoretical mean, <emphasis effect="italics">μ<sub>x</sub></emphasis>? Explain why or why not.</item>
<item>Which of the two distributions of sample means has the smaller standard deviation? Why?</item>
